    • Field Detail

      • ABOUT_DEVICE_ID

        static final String ABOUT_DEVICE_ID
        Required. If Config service exists on the device, About instance populates the DeviceId as per Config service; If there is no Config on the device, it is set using the platform specific means
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • ABOUT_DEVICE_NAME

        static final String ABOUT_DEVICE_NAME
        Required. If Config service exists on the device, About instance populates the value as DeviceName in Config; If there is no Config, it is set by platform specific means and reflected in About
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • ABOUT_APP_ID

        static final String ABOUT_APP_ID
        Required. The globally unique id for the application
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • ABOUT_APP_NAME

        static final String ABOUT_APP_NAME
        Required. This field specifies the Application Name. It is assigned by the App Manufacturer
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • ABOUT_MANUFACTURER

        static final String ABOUT_MANUFACTURER
        Required. The manufacturer's name of the application.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • ABOUT_DESCRIPTION

        static final String ABOUT_DESCRIPTION
        Required. Detailed description
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • ABOUT_DEFAULT_LANGUAGE

        static final String ABOUT_DEFAULT_LANGUAGE
        Required. The default language supported by the device. IETF language tags specified by RFC 5646. It is populated by Config service when present else it is specified by device specific means
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • ABOUT_SOFTWARE_VERSION

        static final String ABOUT_SOFTWARE_VERSION
        Required. The software version for the OEM software.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • ABOUT_AJ_SOFTWARE_VERSION

        static final String ABOUT_AJ_SOFTWARE_VERSION
        Required. The current version of the AllJoyn SDK utilized by the application.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • ABOUT_MODEL_NUMBER

        static final String ABOUT_MODEL_NUMBER
        Required. The application model number.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • ABOUT_DATE_OF_MANUFACTURE

        static final String ABOUT_DATE_OF_MANUFACTURE
        Optional. The date of manufacture using format YYYY-MM-DD (known as XML DateTime Format)
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • ABOUT_HARDWARE_VERSION

        static final String ABOUT_HARDWARE_VERSION
        Optional. The device hardware version
        See Also:

      • ABOUT_SUPPORT_URL

        static final String ABOUT_SUPPORT_URL
        Optional. The support URL to be populated by device OEM
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • ABOUT_SUPPORTED_LANGUAGES

        static final String ABOUT_SUPPORTED_LANGUAGES
